## Recommended minimal changes

### `UserEntity`

Add stable AS400/Ping identifiers and user state:

```java
@Column(name = "gps_group_number", unique = true)
private String gpsGroupNumber;

@Column(name = "source_personal_id")
private String sourcePersonalId;

@Column(name = "entity")
private String entity;

@Column(name = "language")
private String language;

@Column(name = "status", nullable = false)
private String status;
```

Your existing `userId` can be the Partner Repository internal/business user identifier. I would use `gpsGroupNumber` as the stable external match key from AS400.

